Dear Tom, My statements about theory/practice were not just replies to  
you. They had a context too, which it seems you're not entirely     
attending. But I don't want to fight about it. I'm sorry if it seemed I     
was not appreciating all the wisdom and clarity of your thought.    
I'm sorry if my words were to you "no reaction at all." In the future   
I'll try to do better, because it's clear that you're one of the most   
important voices on here, and your judgments are crucial.       
Yrs, Spencer Selby      
P.S. Whatever the context, I don't believe "this discourse proceeds at  
the level of the poetry."       
    
