> many say has become a dangerous place for those who love poetry.      
>     ``This has nothing to do with `Language Poetry','' said   
> Economics Minister Charles Bernstein, ``despite what everyone has     
> been saying.''        
>     ``It's that damned old boys network,'' says Education     
> Minister Susan Howe. ``Not that I have anything against old boys.     
> But enough's enough.''        
