Subject:  refried nombres       
    
`every poem is a theory' is a theory    
& ``every poem is a theory' is a theory'is a theory         
&'& ```every poem is a theory' is a theory' & ``every poem is a     
theory' is a theory'' is a theory.      
    
& there are many more theories      
& '& there are many more theories' is a theory  
& '& '& there are are many more theories' is a theory' is a theory      
