If you would prefer to receive one message from the Poetics list each day,  
which would include all messages posted to the list for that day, you can now   
use the digest option:      
    
Send this one-line message (no subject line) to 
        listserv@ubvm.cc.buffalo.edu    
    
set poetics digest      
    
    
!!Send this message to "listserv" not to Poetics or as a reply to this  
message!!   
    
You can switch back to individual posts by sending this messagage:      
    
set poetics mail        
