 club, Sikelianos has shown a great deal of promise.        
  Hollo has six insights, Sikelianos has three insights and     
 Hawkins has one inspired outburst and four insights for five       
 points in 4 weeks this year. All three players are expected to be      
 in uniform tomorrow night when Buffalo hosts the Southern      
 California Sun & Moons.        
