Subject:  Re: baby logic    
    
jorge, yes, it's that grownup logic IS baby logic, exactly... a knotty  
conundrum, reminds me of mark taylor's disquisitions in _nOts_... the   
tautology "a or not a" hits at precisely this, where "a" is the null    
set... so we opt for something ex nihilo, or the nothing that is there...   
    
what a revoltin' predicament!...    
    
joe     
